OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FIt will be a
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with a few light
OL,7,Fshowers around. Showers dying out
OL,8,Fovernight with some clear spells
OL,9,Fdeveloping leading to a risk of frost
OL,10,Fin places.
OL,11,
OL,12,CMonday:FDry through the morning and
OL,13,Ffor much of the afternoon with good
OL,14,Fsunny spells. Turning cloudy with some
OL,15,Fshowers spreading east through late
OL,16,Fafternoon and evening.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
